    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'textTargets.Array.data[1]'
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 5920779229032263456}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.size
      value: 9
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[0].text
      value: Come now. Sit down and eat
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[1].text
      value: Just sit still and enjoy the food
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].text
      value: "You only have to stay where you\u2019re told"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[3].text
      value: Distractions make people ungrateful
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].text
      value: It becomes easier once you stop deciding things for yourself
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[5].text
      value: I'm sure you don't need to be told again
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[6].text
      value: Let's see how you handle this..
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[7].text
      value: You understand quickly
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[8].text
      value: Some struggle so much against simple kindness
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[9].text
      value: Some struggle so much against simple kindness
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[10].text
      value: They all do. Why won't you.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[11].text
      value: ...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[12].text
      value: If only you could live in my shoes.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[13].text
      value: ...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[14].text
      value: Just get me some ramen
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7333351678017638545, guid: 881952eaccb041445b00930ca06f5091, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[15].text
      value: Just get me some ramen
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
